Name: Average time for Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Total time for Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time for Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Time of Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE Cycle Time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE in cases that later result in Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time for Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE in variants that end without proceeding to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE

Name: Average time it takes Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE after the execution of Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum waiting time to the Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE following Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time until Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE is performed after Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time for Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE compared to the average time for Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time for Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE compared to the minimum time for Request Payment in completed reimbursement cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Cycle Time of Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE relative to the Cycle Time of Payment Handled in variants containing both
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Time elapsed between Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE and Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION in variants where the saved declaration is eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time from Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in successful reimbursement paths that originate from a saved declaration
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
